us drones but also any safety-critical embodied agent operating in unpredictable settings—from search-and-rescue robots to planetary rovers. By shifting the paradigm from 'feature fusion' to 'trust-aware reasoning,' CAMF-Net lays the foundation for cognitively resilient autonomy.",
